Peck's dictionary in my QsConverter program... I don't know what sort
of magic he used to generate it, or if he might have other source
dictionaries that he might be able to use.

<freeman@...> wrote:

> Hi Paul,
>

>

> uploaded by group member jeff_smith_8992. Jeff, are you out there??
>
> Ted
>
>
